title: [SOLVED]820-2532 no power
message:
[B]Board history:[/B]

Customer bought this from eBay, it has been liquid damaged and ultrasonic cleaned already by whoever sold it.
There was no green light so replaced sys_onewire_bilat and over voltage protection now got green light.

[B]Power rails:[/B]

3V42 = 3V42
PPBUS_G3H = 12.6
PP3V3_S5 = 3V3
Where is 5V_S5? Can't find it on power rails page.
